{"type":"message","id":"3387303a","parentId":"8a94224e","timestamp":"2026-03-04T02:00:30.912Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_2rllvf8ihdll_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"query\": \"China A-share real-time stock price quotation ths ifind\",\n  \"total\": 10,\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"ths_ifind.real_time_quotation.v1\",\n      \"name\": \"iFinD 同花顺实时行情 (THS Real-time Quotation)\",\n      \"description\": \"Query real-time quotation data for securities in the 同花顺 (THS) iFinD database, providing real-time market data for financial products including stocks, funds, bonds, and futures, such as real-time prices, trading volumes, price changes, bid/ask quotes, etc. Supports querying various real-time indicators including latest price, price change, trading volume, turnover ratio, market value, and five-level bid/ask quotes.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"codes\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": \"Security codes, multiple codes separated by commas (max 50), e.g., '300033.SZ,600030.SH'\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"indicators\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": \"Indicator list, multiple indicators separated by commas. Options: 'common' (common indicators), 'all' (all indicators), or custom indicator list. Default is 'all'\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"codes\": \"300033.SZ,600030.SH\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"同花顺 (THS) iFinD data provider, offering financial data for Chinese and international markets including stocks, securities, funds, bonds, futures, etc. Supports company announcements, intelligent stock screening, industry analysis, market trend prediction, and more, helping users conduct comprehensive financial data analysis and investment decisions.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 1667.64,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.887\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"ths_ifind.quotation.v1\",\n      \"name\": \"iFinD 同花顺行情 (历史+实时) (THS Quotation)\",\n      \"description\": \"Query historical and real-time quotation data for securities in the 同花顺 (THS) iFinD database, supporting price, trading volume, turnover ratio, and other indicators for various financial products including stocks, funds, bonds, and futures.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"codes\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": \"Security codes, multiple codes separated by commas (max 50), e.g., '300033.SZ,600030.SH'\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"indicators\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": \"Indicator list, comma-separated. Options: 'common' (common indicators), 'all' (all indicators), or custom list. Default is 'all'. Applies to both history and real-time calls.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"startdate\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": \"Start date, formats: 'YYYY-MM-DD', 'YYYY/MM/DD', 'YYYYMMDD'\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"enddate\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": \"End date, formats: 'YYYY-MM-DD', 'YYYY/MM/DD', 'YYYYMMDD'\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"interval\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": \"Time period: 'D' (daily), 'W' (weekly), 'M' (monthly), 'Q' (quarterly), 'S' (semi-annual), 'Y' (yearly), default 'D'\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"cps\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": \"Adjustment method: '1' (no adjustment), '2' (forward), '3' (backward), '6' (forward cash dividend), '7' (backward cash dividend), default '1'\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"fill\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": \"Non-trading day handling: 'Previous' (use previous data), 'Blank' (empty), default 'Previous'\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"provider_description\": \"同花顺 (THS) iFinD data provider, offering financial data for Chinese and international markets including stocks, securities, funds, bonds, futures, etc. Supports company announcements, intelligent stock screening, industry analysis, market trend prediction, and more, helping users conduct comprehensive financial data analysis and investment decisions.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 2750.14,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.9\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"ths_ifind.smart_stock_picking.v1\",\n      \"name\": \"iFinD 同花顺智能选股 (THS Intelligent Stock Picking)\",\n      \"description\": \"同花顺 (THS) intelligent stock picking tool that supports filtering stocks in the market through natural language queries. Users can use descriptive query statements to quickly obtain stock data that meets the criteria, including stock codes, names, company cities, concepts, and detailed explanations.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"searchstring\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": \"Natural language search query, e.g., '属于杭州的deepseek概念公司'\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"provider_description\": \"同花顺 (THS) iFinD data provider, offering financial data for Chinese and international markets including stocks, securities, funds, bonds, futures, etc. Supports company announcements, intelligent stock screening, industry analysis, market trend prediction, and more, helping users conduct comprehensive financial data analysis and investment decisions.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 988.17,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.812\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"ths_ifind.code_converter.v1\",\n      \"name\": \"iFinD 同花顺证券代码转换 (THS Security Code Converter)\",\n      \"description\": \"Convert security codes or security names to 同花顺 (THS) standard code format. Supports querying by security code or security name, can specify security type and market, supports exact match or fuzzy match. Returns converted THS codes and related security information.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"seccode\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": \"Security code, e.g., '000001'. Either seccode or secname\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"secname\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": \"Security name, e.g., '平安银行'. Either seccode or secname\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"mode\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": \"Query mode: 'seccode' (query by code) or 'secname' (query by name)\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"sectype\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": \"Security type, e.g., '001' (stock), default is empty (query all types)\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"market\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": \"Market code, e.g., '212001' (SSE), '212100' (SZSE), default is empty (query all markets)\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"tradestatus\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": \"Trading status: '0' (normal trading), '1' (suspended), '2' (all), default is '0'\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"isexact\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": \"Exact match: '1' (exact match), '0' (fuzzy match), default is '1'\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"mode\": \"seccode\",\n          \"seccode\": \"000001\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"同花顺 (THS) iFinD data provider, offering financial data for Chinese and international markets including stocks, securities, funds, bonds, futures, etc. Supports company announcements, intelligent stock screening, industry analysis, market trend prediction, and more, helping users conduct comprehensive financial data analysis and investment decisions.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 582.28,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.98\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"ths_ifind.etf_constituents.v1\",\n      \"name\": \"iFinD ETF成分股票列表 (ETF Constituent Stock List)\",\n      \"description\": \"Query the constituent stock list of an ETF from 同花顺 (THS) iFinD database. Returns detailed information about each constituent stock including stock code, name, share quantity, cash substitution flag, subscription/redemption premium ratios and fixed substitution amounts. Useful for analyzing ETF composition and tracking ETF holdings.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"thscode\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": \"ETF security code, e.g., '510300.SH', '159001.SZ'\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"date\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": \"Query date. Supported formats: 'YYYY-MM-DD', 'YYYY/MM/DD', 'YYYYMMDD'. Defaults to today.\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"provider_description\": \"同花顺 (THS) iFinD data provider, offering financial data for Chinese and international markets including stocks, securities, funds, bonds, futures, etc. Supports company announcements, intelligent stock screening, industry analysis, market trend prediction, and more, helping users conduct comprehensive financial data analysis and investment decisions.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 644.44,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.91\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"ths_ifind.financial_statements.v1\",\n      \"name\": \"iFinD 同花顺财报 Financial Statements (Balance/Income/Cash Flow)\",\n      \"description\": \"Query balance sheet, income statement, or cash flow statement data for securities from THS iFinD Financial Statement database using a single entry point.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"statement_type\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": \"Which statement to query: 'balance', 'income', or 'cash_flow'\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"codes\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": \"Security codes, multiple codes separated by commas (max 50), e.g., '300033.SZ,600030.SH'\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"year\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": \"Year, e.g., '2024'\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"period\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": \"Reporting period: '0331' (Q1), '0630' (H1), '0930' (Q3), '1231' (Annual)\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"type\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": \"Report type: '1' (Consolidated), '2' (Parent Company), '3' (Consolidated Adjusted), '4' (Parent Company Adjusted)\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"provider_description\": \"同花顺 (THS) iFinD data provider, offering financial data for Chinese and international markets including stocks, securities, funds, bonds, futures, etc. Supports company announcements, intelligent stock screening, industry analysis, market trend prediction, and more, helping users conduct comprehensive financial data analysis and investment decisions.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 654.98,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.877\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"ths_ifind.report_query.v1\",\n      \"name\": \"iFinD 同花顺证券公告查询 (THS Security Announcement Query)\",\n      \"description\": \"Query security announcements in the 同花顺 (THS) iFinD database, supporting filtering and searching by security code, date range, and keywords. Users can input security codes (e.g., '920000.BJ'), announcement keywords (e.g., 'annual report'), and date ranges (e.g., '2024-10-25' to '2025-10-25') to quickly obtain detailed information about relevant announcements, including announcement date, security code, security name, release time, announcement title, announcement link, and unique identifier.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"codes\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": \"Security code, multiple codes separated by commas (max 50), e.g., '920000.BJ'\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"keyword\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": \"Announcement keyword for searching announcement titles, default is empty string\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"beginrDate\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": \"Start date, format: 'YYYY-MM-DD'\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"endrDate\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": \"End date, format: 'YYYY-MM-DD'\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"codes\": \"920000.BJ\",\n          \"endrDate\": \"2025-10-25\",\n          \"beginrDate\": \"2024-10-25\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"同花顺 (THS) iFinD data provider, offering financial data for Chinese and international markets including stocks, securities, funds, bonds, futures, etc. Supports company announcements, intelligent stock screening, industry analysis, market trend prediction, and more, helping users conduct comprehensive financial data analysis and investment decisions.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 812.59,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.441\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"ths_ifind.company_basics.v1\",\n      \"name\": \"iFinD 公司基础信息 (Company Basics)\",\n      \"description\": \"Retrieve the latest (or a specific date) company basics indicators from THS iFinD. Includes company name, industry, comparable/peer companies, concept tags, codes, established date, registration info, main business, and major products.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"codes\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": \"Security codes, comma-separated (max 50), e.g., '300033.SZ,600030.SH'\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"date\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": \"Date, format: 'YYYYMMDD'. Use this field to query historical values. Defaults to latest.\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"provider_description\": \"同花顺 (THS) iFinD data provider, offering financial data for Chinese and international markets including stocks, securities, funds, bonds, futures, etc. Supports company announcements, intelligent stock screening, industry analysis, market trend prediction, and more, helping users conduct comprehensive financial data analysis and investment decisions.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 780.08,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.914\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"ths_ifind.balance_sheet.v1\",\n      \"name\": \"iFinD Balance Sheet - Financial Statement (财报_资产负债表)\",\n      \"description\": \"Query balance sheet data for securities from THS iFinD Financial Statement database. Retrieve comprehensive balance sheet indicators including assets, liabilities, and equity data. Supports quarterly (Q1/0331), semi-annual (H1/0630), Q3 (0930), and annual (Y/1231) reports with multiple report types (consolidated, parent company, adjusted).\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"codes\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": \"Security codes, multiple codes separated by commas (max 50), e.g., '300033.SZ,600030.SH'\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"year\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": \"Year, e.g., '2024'\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"period\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": \"Reporting period: '0331' (Q1), '0630' (H1), '0930' (Q3), '1231' (Annual)\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"type\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": \"Report type: '1' (Consolidated), '2' (Parent Company), '3' (Consolidated Adjusted), '4' (Parent Company Adjusted)\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"type\": \"1\",\n          \"year\": \"2024\",\n          \"codes\": \"300033.SZ,600030.SH\",\n          \"period\": \"1231\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"同花顺 (THS) iFinD data provider, offering financial data for Chinese and international markets including stocks, securities, funds, bonds, futures, etc. Supports company announcements, intelligent stock screening, industry analysis, market trend prediction, and more, helping users conduct comprehensive financial data analysis and investment decisions.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 658.95,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.9\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"ths_ifind.hk_connect_stats.v1\",\n    